00:00:36.060 --> 00:00:37.760
that she knows
you have access to.

00:00:38.750 --> 00:00:41.170
Do you act like the hero
and provide your credentials,

00:00:41.170 --> 00:00:42.480
knowing very well that doing

00:00:42.480 --> 00:00:44.980
so could violate our information
security policies

00:00:45.500 --> 00:00:48.290
or do you refer the colleague
to our IT Department,

00:00:48.290 --> 00:00:50.630
